
  Required to have Class 3 license.
  Past experiences in driving small lorries (e.g. Toyota Dyna 10ft Truck)
  Be able to assist with delivery of heavy goods
  Generally fit and healthy
  Able to workover overtime(OT)/during holidays 
  Candidates staying around Jurong West (predominantly west-side) is preferred
  Be proactive and show initiative during deliveries
  When there are no deliveries, help out with simple tasks in the factory
  Maintain a proper upkeep of the lorry
  Able to communicate in english

Note: Drivers are not allowed to drive back with lorry.

